WEBVTT

30:43.200 --> 30:45.760 line:80%
He submits to Wei Yan solely
for the sake of the Imperial Court

30:45.760 --> 30:47.440 line:80%
and the people.

30:47.440 --> 30:50.550 line:80%
But it was because of Wei Yan's
groundless suspicion

30:50.960 --> 30:54.760 line:80%
that he ended up in prison.
